original: Larson, Oscar Arvid, kontorschef, Göteborg, f. 5/9/82 i Gbg. G. 25 m. Ingeborg Swalander. Barn: Kerstin f. 28. — Stud. v. h. allm. lärov. samt han-delssk. Medarb. i firma James Lundgren & Co. i Gbg sed. 20, kontxhef där.
translated: Larson, Oscar Arvid, office manager, Gothenburg, b. 9/5/82 in Gothenburg. Married on the 25th of (unknown year) to Ingeborg Swalander. Children: Kerstin b. 28. — Studied at the public school and business school. Employee at the company James Lundgren & Co. in Gothenburg since 1920, office manager there.
